Package angryflappybird

Class Defines

java.lang.Object
angryflappybird.Defines
public class Defines extends Object
This class contains constants and values used throughout the Angry Flappy Bird game. It defines the dimensions,coefficients for the game objects. It also contains the paths to the image and sound resources used in the game, as well as the media objects and nodes that are part of the game's scene graph
Author:
Robin Tran, Jennifer Pham
